To estimate the total health loss due to delayed access, we first calculate the QALY loss per patient:

\[ \text{QALY}_{\text{lost, per patient}} = \Delta \text{QALY} \times \text{waiting time (years)} \]

analysis_data <- analysis_data %>%
  mutate(qaly_lost_per_patient = delta_qaly * wait_years)
analysis_data %>%
  select(id_nummer, delta_qaly, wait_years, qaly_lost_per_patient) %>%
  head()

We then multiply this value by the size of the patient population to obtain the total QALY loss:

\[ \text{Total QALY loss} = \text{QALY}_{\text{lost, per patient}} \times \text{population} \]

# Total QALY loss = QALY lost per patient × patient population
analysis_data <- analysis_data %>%
  mutate(qaly_lost = qaly_lost_per_patient * population)
analysis_data %>%
  select(id_nummer, qaly_lost_per_patient, population, qaly_lost) %>%
  head()
analysis_data %>%
  arrange(desc(qaly_lost_per_patient)) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = reorder(id_nummer, -qaly_lost_per_patient), y = qaly_lost_per_patient)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity", fill = "#345e7d", width = 0.7) +
  labs(
    title = "QALY Loss per Patient by Drug",
    subtitle = "Sorted by highest individual loss due to delay",
    x = "Drug ID",
    y = "QALY Loss per Patient"
  ) +
  theme_minimal(base_size = 13) +
  theme(
    axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 45, hjust = 1),
    plot.title = element_text(face = "bold")
  )

rabatt_scenarier <- c(0.30, 0.40, 0.48, 0.50)  

sensitivitet_data <- purrr::map_dfr(rabatt_scenarier, function(rabatt) {
  analysis_data %>%
    mutate(
      rabatt_nivå = paste0(rabatt * 100, "%"),
      delta_cost_rabattert = delta_cost * (1 - rabatt),
      avoided_cost = delta_cost_rabattert * population * wait_years,
      cost_per_qaly_lost = avoided_cost / qaly_lost,
      cost_per_qaly_lost_mnok = cost_per_qaly_lost / 1e6,
      threshold_mnok = threshold / 1e6,
      over_threshold = cost_per_qaly_lost > threshold
    )
})
library(gt)

sensitivitet_data %>%
  mutate(
    avoided_cost_mn = round(avoided_cost / 1e6, 1),
    qaly_lost = round(qaly_lost, 1),
    cost_per_qaly_lost_mnok = round(cost_per_qaly_lost_mnok, 2),
    status = ifelse(over_threshold, "❌ Over", "✅ Under")
  ) %>%
  select(rabatt_nivå, id_nummer, qaly_lost, avoided_cost_mn, cost_per_qaly_lost_mnok, threshold_mnok, status) %>%
  gt() %>%
  tab_header(title = "Sensitivity Analysis: Cost per QALY Lost vs. Threshold") %>%
  cols_label(

    status = "Above Threshold?"
  )

beregn_cost_per_qaly <- function(rabatt, delta_cost, pop, wait_years, qaly_lost) {
  rabattert_cost <- delta_cost * (1 - rabatt)
  avoided_cost <- rabattert_cost * pop * wait_years
  avoided_cost / qaly_lost
}

rabatt_seq <- seq(0, 0.8, by = 0.01)

plot_data <- tibble(
  rabatt = rabatt_seq,
  cost_per_qaly = sapply(rabatt_seq, beregn_cost_per_qaly,
                         delta_cost = delta_cost_avg,
                         pop = population_avg,
                         wait_years = wait_years_avg,
                         qaly_lost = qaly_lost_avg)
)
optimal_point <- plot_data %>%
  mutate(diff = abs(cost_per_qaly - threshold_avg)) %>%
  arrange(diff) %>%
  slice(1)

Waitingtime_Analyse_Final <- readRDS("Waitingtime_Analyse_Final.rds")
qaly_loss_table <- analysis_data %>%
  filter(id_nummer %in% c("ID2018_125", "ID2020_112", "ID2020_106", "ID2018_005", "ID2019_044")) %>%
  select(id_nummer, qaly_lost, avoided_cost)
# Slå sammen på ID
qaly_tap_tid <- qaly_loss_table %>%
  left_join(
    Waitingtime_Analyse_Final %>%
      select(id_number, passiv_tid, aktiv_tid, mt_final_decision_num),
    by = c("id_nummer" = "id_number")
  )
qaly_tap_tid <- qaly_tap_tid %>%
  mutate(
    total_tid = passiv_tid + aktiv_tid,
    andel_passiv = passiv_tid / total_tid,
    qaly_tap_passiv = qaly_lost * andel_passiv,
    qaly_tap_aktiv = qaly_lost * (1 - andel_passiv)
  )
qaly_tap_tid %>%
  summarise(
    total_qaly = sum(qaly_lost, na.rm = TRUE),
    passiv_qaly = sum(qaly_tap_passiv, na.rm = TRUE),
    andel_passiv = passiv_qaly / total_qaly
  )
library(dplyr)
library(purrr)

justeringsnivåer <- seq(0, 1.3, by = 0.1)

# Lag sensitivitetstabell
qaly_sensitivitet <- map_dfr(justeringsnivåer, function(p) {
  qaly_tap_tid %>%
    mutate(
      passiv_tid_justert = passiv_tid * p,
      total_tid_justert = passiv_tid_justert + aktiv_tid,
      andel_passiv_justert = passiv_tid_justert / total_tid_justert,
      qaly_passiv_justert = qaly_lost * andel_passiv_justert,
      justeringsfaktor = p
    ) %>%
    summarise(
      justeringsfaktor = unique(justeringsfaktor),
      total_qaly_passiv = sum(qaly_passiv_justert, na.rm = TRUE)
    )
})
max_val <- max(qaly_sensitivitet$total_qaly_passiv, na.rm = TRUE)
min_val <- min(qaly_sensitivitet$total_qaly_passiv, na.rm = TRUE)
# Beregn min_val og max_val før ggplot
min_val <- min(qaly_sensitivitet$total_qaly_passiv, na.rm = TRUE)
max_val <- max(qaly_sensitivitet$total_qaly_passiv, na.rm = TRUE)

  geom_point(data = filter(qaly_sensitivitet, justeringsfaktor == 1.3),
             aes(x = justeringsfaktor, y = total_qaly_passiv),
             color = "darkred", size = 4) +
  geom_text(data = filter(qaly_sensitivitet, justeringsfaktor == 1.3),
            aes(label = "Prolonged Delay (+30%)"),
            vjust = -0.8, color = "darkred", size = 3) +

  geom_vline(xintercept = 1, linetype = "dashed", color = "black") +
  annotate("text", x = 1, y = max_val + 60, label = "Baseline (100%)", 
           hjust = -0.1, size = 4, fontface = "italic") +

  expand_limits(y = max_val + 100) +
  scale_x_continuous(
    breaks = seq(0, 1.3, by = 0.1),
    labels = paste0(seq(0, 1.3, by = 0.1) * 100, "%"),
    limits = c(0, 1.3)
  ) +
  scale_y_continuous(labels = comma) +
  labs(
    title = "Passive QALY Loss under Varying Documentation Delay Scenarios",
    x = "Passive Time Adjustment",
    y = "Total QALYs Lost (Passive Phase)"
  ) +
  theme_minimal(base_size = 13) +
  theme(
    plot.title = element_text(face = "bold", size = 14, hjust = 0.5),
    axis.title = element_text(face = "bold"),
    plot.margin = margin(10, 20, 10, 10)
  ) +
  coord_cartesian(clip = "off")
plot_qaly

ggsave("qaly_sensitivity_plot.pdf", plot = plot_qaly,
       width = 10, height = 6, dpi = 300)  # <- no device argument
